Amavisd-new Puppet Module
=========================

This module will set up basic amavisd-new.
In the debian class custom configuration will be setup, to check for spam and viruses.
For an integration into Postfix and a sample setup, check the README from the Postfix Puppet module.

Configuration (Debian)
----------------------

Class parameters

$viruscheck  : enables virus checks if true
$spamcheck   : enables spam checks if true

Configuration (Debian)
----------------------
Deploy whole /etc/amavisd/amavisd.conf

